          </span>
         </td>
        </tr>
       </table>
       <p class="ltx_p">
        where
        xt
        represents the share price of Day
        t
        , and the
        Measured Stock Volatility
        from Day
        t
        to
        t+œÑ
        :
       </p>
       <table class="ltx_equationgroup ltx_eqn_align" id="Sx1.EGx10">
